HEADWORD: Ladys bedstraw
<hw>La"dy's bed"straw`</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <fld>(Bot.)</fld> <def>The
common bedstraw (<spn>Galium verum</spn>); also, a slender-leaved East
Indian shrub (<spn>Pharnaceum Mollugo</spn>), with white flowers in
umbels.</def>⟦br⟧
